<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3960">‌عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ هَاشِمٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">‌يَحْيَى </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٠٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4894">‌عَمْرُو بْنُ مُرَّةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">‌سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4677">‌عُمَرَ </a>رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهُ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كُلٌّ قَدْ كَانَ خَمْسًا وَأَرْبَعًا، فَأَمَرَ بِأَرْبَعٍ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>